  <h1>@uiloos/alpine 1.4.0</h1>

  <p>Released on <span class="font-mono">2023-10-13</span></p>

  <p>
    The initial release of the Alpine bindings for the "uiloos" library.
  </p>

  <p>
    @uiloos/alpine contains functions which create Alpine data components
    and stores, that subscribe to changes in a uiloos class.
  </p>

  <p>
    For example it contains a function called <a href="/api/alpine/activelist/" class="high underline">activeList</a> which
    you can register to alpine with <span class="high">Alpine.data</span>, allowing you to use <a href="/api/core/activelist/" class="high underline">ActiveList</a>
    from within HTML.
  </p>

  <p>
    Whenever the ActiveList changes Alpine will get notified it needs to re-render, keeping 
    your HTML up to date.
  </p>

  <p>
    For more information go to the <a class="underline" href="/api/alpine">Alpine API</a> page.
  </p>
